name: teamProfile
description: -My motivation was to create code that allows a user to launch a website showing their team using the console to input the data. -I built this project so that I could learn how to create team profile website utilizing express and node as well as writing code to pass tests. -The problem that I solved were the display of data, making sure the tests passed, and that the information was correctly displayed. -I learned about TDD, express, and node.
